        <abstract>
            <p>Is collecting facts on variation; questions AG on the alpine flora of the U. S.</p> 
<p>Sends a list of plants from AG’s <hi rend="italic">Manual of botany</hi> [1848] and asks him to append the ranges of the species.</p> 
        </abstract>
